metadata.name: Music NFT Pack #1
metadata.description:
This token is verifiable for the following incentive:

1. 1% of the streaming royalties of the song attached to their NFT.

The genesis collection is complete. NFTs with higher streaming royalties will be found in the Rap Pack Music Vault collection.

Spotify Playlist of songs within this collection: https://open.spotify.com/playlist/5HbsxXPA5g7P3STfTPHxc1?si=0f94a732bbad4cf0.

You can find out more information on Rap Pack Music NFTs at www.rappacknfts.xyz.

Join the RP server discord to process & claim your royalties. Discord: https://discord.gg/cJWABUmHeX.
